{
  "id": "ps-managed",
  "title": "PS-Managed Access (3-party)",
  "description": "The resource issues a resource token whose aud is the agent's Person Server URL \u2014 not an AS. The agent sends the resource token to the PS, and the PS issues the auth token directly. No Access Server is involved. The auth token's iss is the PS itself.",
  "spec_section": "\u00a7 PS-Managed Access (Three-Party)",
